promise me you can find
him and bring him in?

12:56.202 --> 12:58.238
Can I? Yes. You gonna
charge the case or not?

12:58.238 --> 12:59.806
I'm gonna
prosecutorial-discretion it.

12:59.806 --> 13:01.341
