Suarez has four guys.

13:01.341 --> 13:02.809
I'm just asking for one.

13:02.809 --> 13:04.511
Maybe <i>you</i> guys should
have gone to law school.

13:04.511 --> 13:06.212
No, I wanted to work
for a living.

13:06.212 --> 13:07.380
And here we are.

13:07.380 --> 13:09.482
Thank you.

13:09.482 --> 13:11.651
You still coming
to my party?

13:11.651 --> 13:13.253
I don't know.
You gonna be there?

13:13.253 --> 13:14.654
A full bar
is gonna be there.

13:14.654 --> 13:17.591
Plus, specialty cocktails
with themes.

13:17.591 --> 13:19.926
Ooh! At least
that's fuckin' stupid.

13:37.277 --> 13:38.578
Excuse me, sir. Hmm.

13:38.578 --> 13:40.280
There's no eating
in the courtroom.

13:40.280 --> 13:43.383
No, there's no <i>you</i> eating
in the courtroom. Just me.

13:43.383 --> 13:44.651
You're not me.

13:44.651 --> 13:46.920
Sad but true.
Where's Conchita?

13:46.920 --> 13:49.456
Double-booked,
but she sent her.

13:49.456 --> 13:51.725
Alice.
Okay.

13:51.725 --> 13:53.660
Or Alex.

13:53.660 --> 13:54.861
Well, which is it?

13:54.861 --> 13:56.696
Hmm.

13:56.696 --> 13:58.365
Someone should ask.

14:10.410 --> 14:13.546
Conchita got stuck upstairs,
said she's really sorry.

14:13.546 --> 14:15.715
I'm Alex Forrest.

14:15.715 --> 14:18.852
Alex. That's alright.
Dan Gallagher.

14:18.852 --> 14:20.920
Yeah, she loves you. Conchita.

14:20.920 --> 14:22.756
Yeah, she lowers
my blood pressure.

14:24.024 --> 14:26.626
So... you up to speed
on everything yet?

14:26.626 --> 14:28.862
Yeah, Conchita's definitely
their point person,

14:28.862 --> 14:31.297
but they know me,
so we're good.

14:33.500 --> 14:35.301
They're nervous.

14:35.301 --> 14:36.836
Well, let's go
talk to them.

14:44.711 --> 14:46.079
How you guys
holding up?

14:46.079 --> 14:48.415
Okay.

14:48.415 --> 14:50.050
Big day.

14:50.050 --> 14:51.851
All the times
I had to remind you

14:51.851 --> 14:54.087
to control
your facial expressions,

14:54.087 --> 14:56.656
hide your anger,
hide your pain,

14:56.656 --> 14:59.759
don't do anything to make
the jury feel bad,

14:59.759 --> 15:02.996
feel sorry for the man
who killed Yalina.

15:04.798 --> 15:07.467
But today this is...

15:16.076 --> 15:18.845
This is the sentencing phase.

15:18.845 --> 15:21.915
This is for the judge.

15:21.915 --> 15:23.683
He needs to know what you lost.

15:23.683 --> 15:26.986
So show him.

15:26.986 --> 15:29.856
If you feel angry, be angry.

15:29.856 --> 15:32.726
If you feel like
you want to cry, you cry.

15:32.726 --> 15:35.395
Today is the day
for all the emotions.

15:35.395 --> 15:37.597
And this is the place.

15:37.597 --> 15:39.733
Okay?
Yeah.

15:39.733 --> 15:41.000
Okay?
Yes.

15:42.569 --> 15:44.504
Thank you.
You're welcome.

15:44.504 --> 15:46.439
Thank you. Thanks.

16:05.598 --> 16:07.066
So, are you doing anything
for the big birthday?

16:07.066 --> 16:08.734
Wife's throwing me
a party.

16:08.734 --> 16:10.002
Nice. My mom wanted to do that
for my dad's 40th,

16:10.002 --> 16:11.837
but he didn't want her
to spend the money.

16:11.837 --> 16:13.405
If I was a wiser man,
I'd probably be saying
the same thing.

16:13.405 --> 16:14.907
Yeah, but then he had
a stroke the next year,

16:14.907 --> 16:18.644
so shouldn't have asked him;
should've just done it.

16:18.644 --> 16:20.846
Hi-de-ho, degenerates.

16:20.846 --> 16:22.648
Nice pocket square, E.B.

16:22.648 --> 16:24.083
Oh, you like that?

16:24.083 --> 16:26.619
Oh, what could possibly
go wrong with that?

16:31.991 --> 16:34.160
Victim services.
She works with Conchita.

16:34.160 --> 16:36.095
Conchita, man.
Conchita's the best.

16:36.095 --> 16:37.763
What's her name?

16:39.565 --> 16:41.133
Alice, I think?

16:41.133 --> 16:43.435
Hmm.
Is Alice my big toe?

16:43.435 --> 16:46.038
'Cause I want to bang her on
every piece of furniture I own.

16:48.440 --> 16:50.442
She wants
full overlay now.
Wait. What?

16:50.442 --> 16:52.545
Yeah, her friend Sharon
just had wood inserts put on

16:52.545 --> 16:54.713
all <i>her</i> appliances so they'll
blend with her cabinetry.

16:54.713 --> 16:57.049
Well, speaking of
new appliances,

16:57.049 --> 16:59.819
she wants a cheese
refrigerator now, too.
No, no.

16:59.819 --> 17:02.588
People are feeling a way
about cheese these days, Danny.

17:02.588 --> 17:03.756
Is that way constipated?

17:03.756 --> 17:04.990
It will be.

17:04.990 --> 17:07.193
Oh, hold.

17:07.193 --> 17:09.461
Hi. No, not yet.

17:09.461 --> 17:12.598
Uh, I'm--
I'm coming right now.

17:12.598 --> 17:15.467
Nope.
I forgot. Sorry.

17:15.467 --> 17:17.837
Here. You ask her.
For you.

17:17.837 --> 17:20.139
Let me clean this shit up.
Hey, pal.

